data.name: grdPatient.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.BUNHO BUNHO , A.SUNAME SUNAME , A.SEX SEX , A.BIRTH BIRTH , A.ZIP_CODE1 ZIP_CODE1 , A.ZIP_CODE2 ZIP_CODE2 , A.ADDRESS1 ADDRESS1 , A.ADDRESS2 ADDRESS2 , A.TEL TEL , A.TEL1 TEL1 , A.GUBUN GUBUN , A.TEL_HP TEL_HP , A.EMAIL EMAIL , FN_BAS_LOAD_GUBUN_NAME(A.GUBUN, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) GUBUN_NAME , DECODE(A.ADDRESS2, NULL, NULL, NULL) DONG_NAME , A.SUNAME2 , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(SYSDATE, A.BIRTH, ' ') , A.TEL_GUBUN , A.TEL_GUBUN2 , A.TEL_GUBUN3 , NVL(A.DELETE_YN, 'N') , A.PACE_MAKER_YN , A.SELF_PACE_MAKER , A.BUNHO_TYPE BUNHO_TYPE , 'Y' RETRIEVE_YN FROM OUT0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho

data.name: grdBoheom.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.START_DATE , A.BUNHO , D.SUNAME , A.GUBUN , FN_BAS_LOAD_GUBUN_NAME(A.GUBUN, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) GUBUN_NAME , A.JOHAP , FN_BAS_LOAD_JOHAP_NAME(A.GUBUN, A.JOHAP, A.START_DATE) JOHAP_NAME , '' TEL , A.GAEIN , A.GAEIN_NO , A.BON_GA_GUBUN , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('BON_GA_GUBUN', A.BON_GA_GUBUN) BONIN_GUBUN_NAME , A.PINAME , A.LAST_CHECK_DATE , A.END_DATE , E.JOHAP_GUBUN , A.GUBUN OLD_GUBUN , 'Y' RETRIEVE_YN , A.START_DATE OLD_START_DATE , A.CHUIDUK_DATE CHUIDUK_DATE , CASE WHEN A.END_DATE < TRUNC(SYSDATE) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END END_YN FROM BAS0210 E , OUT0101 D , OUT0102 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.BUNHO = D.BUNHO AND A.GUBUN = E.GUBUN --AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN E.START_DATE AND E.END_DATE ORDER BY TO_CHAR(A.START_DATE, 'YYYYMMDD') || A.GUBUN DESC

data.name: grdGongbiList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.START_DATE START_DATE , A.BUNHO , A.BUDAMJA_BUNHO , A.GONGBI_CODE , A.SUGUBJA_BUNHO , A.END_DATE , A.REMARK , A.LAST_CHECK_DATE , B.GONGBI_NAME , 'Y' RETRIEVE_YN , A.START_DATE OLD_START_DATE , CASE WHEN A.END_DATE < TRUNC(SYSDATE) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END END_YN FROM BAS0212 B , OUT0105 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.GONGBI_CODE = B.GONGBI_CODE AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE ORDER BY A.GONGBI_CODE
